  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a central courtyard and the flat and the block of-- the apartment block formed a kind of a rectangle around the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the courtyard was reached by a entrance hall from the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You went into the-- there was a big gate at the-- in the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then through that gate, you came into a kind of vaulting into a kind of a little tunnel and there usually was the entrance to the main staircase, the staircase leading to the apartments, which were in the front part of the house, out facing the street.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Those were usually the best apartments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then you walk through this vaulting, you came to a large, large courtyard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the houses were-- and the house, the block was in a rectangle around the courtyard with usually something like maybe three or four staircases, on each side, a staircase.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on the staircase in the back, and each staircase went up five or six floors and, and, and, and on each floor, you had three or four apartments, entered from the-- from the common hall.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was a lot of life happening in the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the courtyard, people were coming and going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all kinds of beggars, or street beggars were coming there and playing music.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And later, children in ghetto-- children would come as well and say their-- their things, ask for, for, for charity.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And well, carpets were, were, were cleaned and, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was-- and this apartment was not beautiful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember dark and our-- and our-- and our furniture still from before the war, some of it, at least.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
